.SH NAME
ztai-portal \- run and operate the zero-trust paywalled web portal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ztai-portal
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The Zero-Trust AI Defense Portal serves a web UI at /app with a paywall. It supports Stripe Checkout, registration with verification, and Redis-backed sessions.
.SH CONFIGURATION
.TP
.B STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
Stripe secret API key.
.TP
.B STRIPE_PRICE_ID
Stripe price ID for the product/plan.
.TP
.B STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
Stripe webhook signing secret.
.TP
.B STRIPE_MODE
"payment" (default) or "subscription".
.TP
.B ENABLE_DEV_PAY
Enable dev simulate payment (1/0). Default 1.
.TP
.B RETURN_VERIFICATION_CODE
Return verification code from /register/start in dev (1/0). Default 1.
.TP
.B REDIS_URL
Redis connection URL for sessions and registration.
.TP
.B SESSION_TTL
Session TTL in seconds. Default 604800.
.SH FILES
.I web/index.html
.RS
Portal UI.
.RE
.I server/protected_server.py
.RS
FastAPI app with endpoints.
.RE
.I server/paywall.py
.RS
Session and paywall manager.
.RE
.I server/registration.py
.RS
Registration and verification manager.
.RE
